In this case, could you please consider the following changes,

Create a TaskResourceComputationStage, because we the reuse logic has been reduced quite a lot. It is no longer reasonable to put all logic in one class.
If another class is too much, we should at least make the workflow clean to fit the following structure:
if (taskCache) {
// process TF Resource Objects...
} else {
// process Regular Resource Objects...
}
// Read the current state to backfill any resources that need to be removed.

